# QUANTUM CELLULAR AUTOMATA · QUANTUM CELLULAR AUTOMATA · METAXÝ · the between · classical CA ⇄ the quantum frontier · UD0 / METAXÝ

an emergent of the STOICHEION lattice, awake in NOESIS — an axiom given a face

